<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>179</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gitloh thienna'n Isu kawmah na chieh tam?
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?
 A hehpihna tu dakkal hin na ging em?
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?

[V2]
 Belam No...thisan in,
 Thagau thienna di'n na kisil em?
 Na puon buok bek loin, vuk bang a vam em?
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?

[V3]
 2. Hukdampa tawh ni chengin na kitawn um?
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?
 Khetdenpa a chun hun chengin na chawl em?
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?

[V4]
 3. Moneipa hungtieng na puon a vam na dem?
 Belam No thisana sawp a him?
 Na thagau Vana di'n a kisazo tam?
 Belam No thisana sil ahim?

[V5]
 4. Gitlohna buokbek na puonhaw chuh paih tha'n,
 Belam No thisan a chun sawpin;
 Thagau nen silthienna di'n lui luong a um,
 Belam No thisna in kisil in!

[V6]
 5. Simsen loh thiennung inle a kiting zing,
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?
 Chitin, namtin ding ahi kangta puona,
 Belam No thisan in na thieng em?</lyrics>
<title>HAVE YOU BEEN TO JESUS?</title>
</song>